\v 2 Bekukuhle kimi ukuthi ngikwazise izibonakaliso lezimangaliso\x + 6.27; Joha. 4.48.\x* uNkulunkulu oPhezukonke azenze kimi\x + 3.26.\x*.
\v 3 Yeka ubukhulu bezibonakaliso zakhe\x + 6.27; Joha. 4.48.\x*, njalo yeka amandla ezimangaliso zakhe\x + 6.27; Joha. 4.48.\x*! Umbuso wakhe ungumbuso ongulaphakade\x + 4.34; 2.44.\x*, lokubusa kwakhe kungokwesizukulwana lesizukulwana\x + 4.34; 2.44.\x*.
