\v 6 Ngakho umlayo wenziwa yimi\x + 3.29.\x* wokuthi kungeniswe phambi kwami\x + 2.2; 5.7.\x* bonke abahlakaniphileyo beBhabhiloni\x + 4.18; 2.12.\x*, ukuze bangazise ingcazelo yephupho.
\v 7 Kwasekungena izanuse, izangoma, amaKhaladiya\x + 2.2; 5.7.\x*, labalumbi\x + 2.27.\x*; ngasengikhuluma iphupho phambi kwabo, kodwa kabangazisanga ingcazelo yalo\x + 4.18; 2.27; 5.8.\x*.
