\v 8 Kodwa ngasekucineni uDaniyeli wangena phambi kwami, obizo lakhe lalinguBeliteshazari\x + 1.7.\x*, ngokwebizo likankulunkulu wami, lokukuye umoya wabonkulunkulu abangcwele\x + 4.9,18; 5.11,14; Isa. 63.11; 2.11; Gen. 41.38.\x*; ngasengikhuluma iphupho phambi kwakhe, \add ngisithi\x + 4.31; Eks. 18.4.\x*\add*:
\v 9 Wena Beliteshazari\x + 1.7.\x*, nduna yezanuse\x + 5.11; 2.48.\x*, ngoba mina ngiyazi ukuthi umoya wabonkulunkulu abangcwele ukuwe\x + 9,18; 5.11,14; Isa. 63.11; 2.11; Gen. 41.38.\x*, lokuthi kakulamfihlakalo leyodwa ekuhluphayo\x + 2.18.\x*, \add ngi\add*tshela imibono yephupho lami engilibonileyo\x + 10,13; 2.28.\x*, lengcazelo yalo.
\v 10 Yayinjalo imibono yekhanda lami embhedeni wami\x + 10,13; 2.28.\x*: Ngabona, khangela-ke\x + Hez. 31.3; Dan. 4.20-26.\x*, isihlahla phakathi komhlaba, lobude baso babubukhulu.
\v 11 Isihlahla sakhula saba sikhulu, saqina, lobude baso bafinyelela emazulwini, lokubonakala kwaso kwaze kwaba sekucineni komhlaba wonke.
\v 12 Amahlamvu aso ayemahle\x + 4.21.\x*, lesithelo saso sasisinengi\x + 4.21.\x*, kwakukhona kiso\x + 4.21.\x* ukudla kwabo bonke\x + Gen. 45.23.\x*; inyamazana zeganga zaba lomthunzi ngaphansi kwaso\x + 4.21.\x*\x + Lilo 4.20; Hez. 17.23; 31.6.\x*, lenyoni zamazulu zahlala ezingatsheni zaso\x + 4.21.\x*, layo yonke inyama yondliwa kiso.
\v 13 Ngabona emibonweni yekhanda lami embhedeni wami\x + 4.10,13; 2.28.\x*, khangela-ke, umlindi\x + 4.17,23; Hlab. 103.20.\x*, ngitsho ongcwele, wehla evela emazulwini\x + 4.23; 4.17; Dute. 33.2,3; 7.18,21,22,25,27; 8.13; Zek. 14.5. Juda 14.\x*.
\v 14 Wamemeza ngamandla watsho njalo: Sigamuleni isihlahla\x + 4.23; Mat. 3.10.\x*, liqume izingatsha zaso\x + Hez. 31.12.\x*, liphulule amahlamvu aso, lichithachithe izithelo zaso; izinyamazana kazisuke ngaphansi kwaso\x + Hez. 31.12.\x*, lezinyoni ngasezingatsheni zaso.
\v 15 Lanxa kunjalo tshiyani isidindi sempande zakhe emhlabathini, langebhanti lensimbi lethusi ohlazeni lwasendle; njalo kakumanziswe ngamazolo amazulu, lesabelo sakhe kasibe kanye lezinyamazana etshanini bomhlaba.
\v 16 Inhliziyo yakhe kayiphenduke ingabi ngeyomuntu, kayiphiwe inhliziyo yenyamazana; futhi kakwedlule phezu kwakhe izikhathi eziyisikhombisa\x + 4.23,25,32; 1 Lan. 29.30; 7.25; 11.13; 12.7.\x*.
\v 17 Loludaba lungesimemezelo\x + 4.24.\x* sabalindi\x + 4.13.\x*, lesilayezelo ngelizwi labangcwele\x + 4.13.\x*; ukuze\x + 2.30.\x* abaphilayo bazi\x + Hlab. 9.16.\x* ukuthi\x + 4.25,32; 5.21.\x* oPhezukonke\x + 4.25,32;5.21.\x* uyabusa embusweni wabantu\x + 2.21; Hlab. 47.2; 83.18; 103.19.\x*, njalo\x + 4.25,32; 5.21.\x* awunike loba kukubani amthandayo\x + Jer. 27.5; 5.18.\x*, amise phezu kwawo ophansi ebantwini\x + 1 Sam. 2.8; Hlab. 113.7.8; 4.37.\x*.
\v 18 Leliphupho ngilibonile mina nkosi uNebhukadinezari. Wena-ke, Beliteshazari\x + 4.8.\x*, yitsho ingcazelo yalo; ngoba\x + 2.40.\x* bonke abahlakaniphileyo bombuso wami bengelakho ukungitshela ingcazelo\x + Gen. 41.8; Dan. 5.8,15; 4.7.\x*; kodwa wena ulakho; ngoba umoya wabonkulunkulu abangcwele ukuwe\x + 4.8.\x*.
