\v 19 Lapho uDaniyeli, obizo lakhe lalinguBeliteshazari\x + 4.8.\x*, wamangala kakhulu okwesikhatshana\x + 2 Kor. 7.8; Gal. 2.5; Dan.4.33; 5.5.\x*, lemicabango yakhe yamkhathaza\x + 5.6.\x*. Inkosi yaphendula, yathi: Beliteshazari, iphupho lengcazelo yalo kakungakukhathazi. UBeliteshazari waphendula wathi: Nkosi yami, iphupho kalibe kwabakuzondayo, lengcazelo yalo kuzo izitha zakho\x + 1 Sam. 25.26; 2 Sam. 18.32.\x*.
\v 20 Isihlahla osibonileyo\x + 4.10,11.\x*, esakhula saba sikhulu saqina, lobude baso bafinyelela emazulwini, lokubonakala kwaso kwaze kwaba semhlabeni wonke,
