\v 22 singuwe, wena nkosi, osukhulile waba mkhulu waqina\x + 2.38.\x*; ngoba ubukhulu bakho bukhulile, bafinyelela emazulwini, lombuso wakho\x + Jer. 27.6-8.\x* ekucineni komhlaba\x + 4.11.\x*.
\v 23 Njengalokho inkosi yabona umlindi\x + 4.13.\x*, ngitsho ongcwele, esehla evela emazulwini owathi: Gamulani isihlahla lisichithe\x + 4.14.\x*; kodwa litshiye isidindi sezimpande emhlabathini\x + 4.15,26.\x* \add sibotshwe\add* ngebhanti lensimbi lethusi ohlazeni lwasendle; kakumanziswe ngamazolo amazulu, lesabelo sakhe kasibe kanye lezinyamazana zeganga, kuze kwedlule izikhathi eziyisikhombisa phezu kwakhe\x + 4.23,25,32; 1 Lan. 29.30; 7.25; 11.13; 12.7.\x*.
