\v 25 Ukuthi bazakuxotsha ebantwini\x + 4.32; 5.21.\x*, lenhlalo yakho izakuba kanye lezinyamazana zeganga, bazakudlisa\x + 4.32; 5.21.\x* utshani\x + Hlab. 106.20.\x* njengezinkabi, bazakumanzisa ngamazolo amazulu, lezikhathi eziyisikhombisa zizadlula phezu kwakho\x + 4.23,25,32; 1 Lan. 29.30; 7.25; 11.13; 12.7.\x*, uze wazi\x + 4.32; 5.21.\x*\x + 2 Lan. 33.13.\x* ukuthi\x + 4.25,32; 5.21.\x* oPhezukonke uyabusa emibusweni yabantu\x + 4.24,25,32,34; 7.25; 3.26.\x*, ayinike loba kukubani amthandayo\x + 4.25,32; 5.21.\x*.
