\v 27 Ngakho, nkosi, kasemukeleke kuwe iseluleko sami\x + 2.6.\x*; wephule izono zakho ngokulunga\x + Mat. 6.1.\x*, lobubi bakho\x + Zaga 16.6.\x* ngokutshengisa isihawu kwabangabayanga\x + Hlab. 41.1; Mat. 25.35; Luka 3.11; 16.9.\x*, aluba\x + Seb. 8.22; 2 Tim. 2.25; Jer. 18.7,8; Jona 3.5.\x* kungaba lokwelulwa\x + 7.12; 1 Kho. 21.29.\x* kokuthula kwakho\x + 4.4.\x*.
